Design Orchestration Graphically

Create fulfillment steps and organize their dependencies directly within an intuitive graphic interface. Set up reusable step groups and order them by clicking and dragging.

Where: This feature is available in Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

How: From the App Launcher, launch Fulfillment Workspaces.
